# Game Boy ROM Sources
# 
# Place this file as /roms/sources.txt on your microSD card.
# One source URL per line. '#' starts a comment.
#
# Supported formats:
#   - Plain text manifests: one ROM URL per line (optionally "Display | URL")
#   - HTML directory listings: all .gb links are auto-extracted
#
# Examples:

# HTML directory with auto-extracted .gb links
https://www.romsgames.net/roms/gameboy/

# Plain text manifests with custom names
# https://example.com/gameboy-roms.txt | My Collection

# More HTML sources
# https://example.org/gb-games/
